    "To measure the richness of the weight updates received by the end of the fine-tuning process, we compare the ranks of ∆W.",
    "Table 15 shows the substantial difference in their ranks.",
    "In the case of LoRA, the weight update (∆W = BA) is constrained to be of rank r = 8.",
    "A similar bound exists in the case of LoRMA + (∆W = BAW 0).",
    "For LoRMA π, no such restriction exists, and the weight update is an almost full rank matrix."
